%% Main Business Flows - Tech Challenge Fase 04
%% This diagram shows the main flows: feedback submission, urgent notification, and weekly report.
%% Language: English

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Student)
    participant API as API Gateway / Serverless Function
    participant DB as Managed Database
    participant Notification as Notification Service
    participant Admin as Admin/Analyst
    participant Report as Report Service

    %% Feedback Submission
    User->>API: POST /avaliacao (feedback)
    API->>DB: Store feedback
    API-->>User: 201 Created (feedback stored)

    %% Urgent Notification Flow
    API->>Notification: Send urgent notification (if needed)
    Notification-->>User: Notify user (urgent case)

    %% Weekly Report Flow
    API->>Report: Trigger weekly report (scheduled)
    Report->>DB: Fetch feedback data
    Report-->>Admin: Send weekly report
